# OpsGateway
An REST gateway exposing OPS features as a sevice

## K8S ConfigMaps [/infr/k8s/configmaps{?namespace}]

### List all ConfigMaps [GET]
List all configuration maps. Allows filtering base on provided labels

+ Parameters
    + namespace: `nrg` (string, required) - Namespace from which ConfigMap should be retruned

    
+ Request A request with valid namespace
    + Parameters 
        + namespace: validNamespace
        
    + Headers
            
            Accept-Version: 1.0.0
            Content-Type: application/json

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    Returns list of ConfigMap associatied with specific namespace when any found
    + Body    
        
            {  
                "data": [
                    {
                        "id": "ps-app-app01-01",
                        "created": "2015-08-05T08:40:51.620Z",
                        "last_updated": "2015-08-05T08:40:51.620Z",
                        "last_modified_by": "user1",
                        "body": "
                            a = 1
                            b = 2
                            c = 3
                        "
                    }
                ], 
                "meta": {
                    "items": 1
                },
                "errors": []
            }
            


